data.description: Welcome Home! This pristine 3 bed 2.5 bath Townhome is located in the sought after Village at Twin Creeks subdivision. As you step inside you can't help but notice it is laced with fresh carpet and fresh neutral paint. You will also notice the large open kitchen with breakfast bar & walk in pantry. The oversized family room is also open to the kitchen and breakfast bar and is perfect for entertaining. Full use of Twin Creeks community amenities & front yard maintenance included with HOA. The location is just as stellar being just minutes from 121 and 75 and conveniently next to various restaurants and shopping.
